_:Ncaf1fa5a403146df95932790aaf6511b <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Abena Oppong-Asare was Parliamentary Secretary at the Cabinet Office between 9 July 2024 and 6 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Erith and Thamesmead in December 2019.</p>\n" .
